01:22:02,940 --> 01:22:03,909
or a birthday. No occasion.

1421
01:22:07,012 --> 01:22:10,116
Just wanted to have
a meal with me,

1422
01:22:10,149 --> 01:22:11,883
and this was a great meal.

1423
01:22:11,917 --> 01:22:15,087
I always say outside jail
this is a normal meal

1424
01:22:15,119 --> 01:22:17,390
but inside Pakistan
this is a five star meal.

1425
01:22:17,422 --> 01:22:19,425
This is the kind of meal you'd
