The government
was trying to help

1481
01:25:43,829 --> 01:25:46,332
but we have a lot of
interests with Pakistan.

1482
01:25:46,364 --> 01:25:49,367
We're allies,
we have military interests,

1483
01:25:49,400 --> 01:25:51,903
