1485
01:25:56,975 --> 01:25:59,144
So there was a lot
of security interests

1486
01:25:59,177 --> 01:26:02,381
and sometimes the U.S.
government doesn't want to

1487
01:26:02,413 --> 01:26:05,216
get those interests in
jeopardy

1488
01:26:05,249 --> 01:26:09,754
by pressing on the release
of a young man like Erik.

1489
01:26:09,788 --> 01:26:14,727
And I felt that I still had
relationships in Pakistan,

1490
01:26:14,760 --> 01:26:16,928
I'd been there many times,

1491
01:26:16,962 --> 01:26:18,964
I knew high level people.

1492
01:26:18,997 --> 01:26:20,633
They had actually
helped me

1493
