"Erik, you're going home."

1530
01:28:03,034 --> 01:28:05,104
And I was like:
"Thank you."

1531
01:28:12,377 --> 01:28:14,213
Sherry, what's going
through your head right now?

1532
01:28:14,245 --> 01:28:18,382
Oh I'm... I'm just trying to
hold myself together.

1533
01:28:18,415 --> 01:28:20,351
I can't believe it's
really happening.

1534
01:28:34,266 --> 01:28:35,901
You alright?

1535
01:28:35,934 --> 01:28:37,770
Erik, how
does it feel to be home?

1536
01:28:37,802 --> 01:28:40,805
It's uh, it's new,
it's wonderful,

1537
01:28:40,838 --> 01:28:42,373
The best Christmas gift
I could ever ask for.

1538
01:28:56,387 --> 01:28:57,989
In that moment
when I saw him,

1539
01:28:58,022 --> 01:28:58,923
it was emotional.

1540
01:29:00,324 --> 01:29:02,126
Usually I don't cry.

1541
01:29:02,159 --> 01:29:03,494
I'm a military guy
I don't...

1542
01:29:03,528 --> 01:29:05,297
But it was rough.

1543
01:29:07,998 --> 01:29:11,903
So good when I saw him,
I just cried.

1544
01:29:11,936 --> 01:29:13,372
I was overcome, you know.

1545
01:29:14,405 --> 01:29:16,441
We were just completely...

1546
01:29:17,475 --> 01:29:19,912
Our breath
was taken away.

1547
01:29:19,945 --> 01:29:21,547
To be able to
see him in person.

1548
01:29:29,387 --> 01:29:32,324
But I understand that Rai
Ghazarian is out there still.

1549
01:29:50,441 --> 01:29:53,412
If Rai was
sitting here right now...

1550
01:29:54,512 --> 01:29:56,582
Honestly I...

1551
01:29:56,614 --> 01:29:58,050
I don't even know
what I would say.

1552
01:29:58,083 --> 01:30:00,118
I'd be
absolutely disgusted.

1553
01:30:00,150 --> 01:30:01,854
I think he's
a horrible person

1554
01:30:01,887 --> 01:30:05,257
that was never punished
for what he did to Erik.

1555
01:30:05,289 --> 01:30:07,959
I think he's heartless

1556
01:30:07,993 --> 01:30:10,529
and I think it's really sad
that he got away with

1557
01:30:10,561 --> 01:30:12,129
what he got away with.

1558
01:30:12,163 --> 01:30:13,566
He hurt a lot of people.

1559
01:30:18,102 --> 01:30:22,073
I hope that God puts him
straight into the Hades.

1560
01:30:23,173 --> 01:30:25,343
I was so mad.
I told his mom:

1561
01:30:25,377 --> 01:30:27,479
"Oh my God, I don't
want to see this guy."

1562
01:30:28,480 --> 01:30:30,015
I just don't
want to see him.

1563
01:30:31,016 --> 01:30:32,184
<i>Have
you ever seen him since?</i>

1564
01:30:32,217 --> 01:30:35,087
Oh my God, never, ever.

1565
01:30:35,119 --> 01:30:37,189
I saw him from the gym
before the incident

1566
01:30:37,221 --> 01:30:38,857
and after that never.

1567
01:30:39,556 --> 01:30:42,026
If I saw that guy I wouldn't
let him go with one choke.

1568
01:30:42,060 --> 01:30:45,364
I'll be honest with you.
Until they take me into jail.

1569
01:30:45,396 --> 01:30:47,031
Because he was sneaky

1570
01:30:47,065 --> 01:30:48,600
and he was an asshole.
From the beginning

1571
01:30:48,632 --> 01:30:51,269
he was planning to
take that person to prison.

1572
01:30:54,672 --> 01:30:57,008
Lorna and I, we found...

