01:32:44,114 --> 01:32:47,519
into present day, did you
guys maintain a friendship

1606
01:32:47,552 --> 01:32:50,556
or try to
have a relationship?

1607
01:32:51,522 --> 01:32:53,357
<i>We
tried shortly, you know.</i>

1608
01:32:53,391 --> 01:32:54,727
<i>We tried when he got home.</i>

1609
01:32:57,494 --> 01:33:01,465
<i>It was hard. I don't
think I fully could be</i>

1610
01:33:01,498 --> 01:33:05,202
<i>the person that he
