1611
01:33:05,235 --> 01:33:08,172
<i>We had these
ideas in our head</i>

1612
01:33:09,306 --> 01:33:11,042
<i>of who the other person was</i>

1613
01:33:11,743 --> 01:33:14,513
<i>and I felt like I could
