1619
01:33:36,266 --> 01:33:37,836
My first couple days back

1620
01:33:37,869 --> 01:33:40,138
I wanted to get
my life back together.

1621
01:33:40,171 --> 01:33:44,309
My high school football coach
he let me use his car.

1622
01:33:44,342 --> 01:33:48,312
I asked him... I told him I'd
