1629
01:34:04,529 --> 01:34:07,165
and I wouldn't...
I didn't want to take it

1630
01:34:07,198 --> 01:34:09,234
and I wouldn't have
taken it either.

1631
01:34:09,266 --> 01:34:12,104
But he's such a massive man, he
was able to put it in my pocket

1632
01:34:12,137 --> 01:34:15,173
and force me into my car
and close the door.

1633
01:34:15,205 --> 01:34:17,242
And I needed
that hundred dollars.

1634
01:34:17,275 --> 01:34:18,610
He knew I needed it.

1635
01:34:19,543 --> 01:34:21,879
But I saw a sign
off the freeway

1636
01:34:21,913 --> 01:34:25,117
