1637
01:34:25,850 --> 01:34:27,651
So I thought, you
know what, I'll kill some time,

1638
01:34:27,685 --> 01:34:30,388
just until
traffic winds down,

1639
01:34:30,421 --> 01:34:32,391
and I'll see what I
can do with fifty dollars.

1640
01:34:34,359 --> 01:34:38,363
I stay all night and I leave
