1645
01:34:49,707 --> 01:34:53,677
<i>It was a traumatic
experience while he was there</i>

1646
01:34:53,711 --> 01:34:56,882
<i>but now he's making the
best of a bad situation.</i>

1647
01:34:58,283 --> 01:35:02,820
<i>I'm just like
really inspired by him.</i>

1648
01:35:02,854 --> 01:35:04,556
That someone can
go through that

1649
01:35:04,588 --> 01:35:07,725
and still come
back the way that he has.

1650
01:35:09,726 --> 01:35:12,897
to see him come back and pick up
where he left off,

1651
01:35:12,931 --> 01:35:16,601
